text: Æræst of Terstan upp on Iww cumb.
Of wænhyrste on ðone ealde iw.
Ðonone of ðon iwe to Lullan setle.
Of Lullan setle to beocera gente.
Of beocere gente to horsweges heale.
Of horsweages heale to æppen lega.
Of fæstan ac on feora burnan æwylman.
Of feora burnan to ceomman bricge.
Of Cæorswylle up to ðam ellene.
